.BR vittec .

This includes:

.TP
.B help
Display help information.

.TP
.B parse
Run lexical and syntactic analysis.

.TP
.B check
Perform semantic validation.

.TP
.B build
Compile source code.

.TP
.B run
Compile and execute.

.TP
.B fmt
Format source code.

.TP
.B lint
Run lints and style checks.

.TP
.B test
Execute tests.

.TP
.B bench
Run benchmarks.

.TP
.B package
Create distributable artifacts.

.TP
.B doc
Generate documentation.

.TP
.B mod
Module management commands.

.TP
.B explain
Explain diagnostic codes.

.TP
.B doctor
Validate toolchain configuration.

