.SH EXAMPLES

Compile:

.nf
vittec build hello.vit
.fi

Run:

.nf
vittec run hello.vit
.fi

Generate LLVM IR:

.nf
vittec build hello.vit --emit-llvm
.fi

Generate assembly:

.nf
vittec build hello.vit --emit-asm
.fi

Check only:

.nf
vittec check hello.vit
.fi

Diagnostics JSON:

.nf
vittec check hello.vit --diag-json
.fi

Arduino:

.nf
vittec build blink.vit \\
  --target arduino-uno \\
  --upload
.fi

.SH MIGRATION

New projects should prefer:

.BR vitte (1)

instead of

.BR vittec .

Existing projects may continue using

.B vittec

without modification.

.SH BUGS

Issues should be reported through the Vitte issue tracker together
with compiler version, target platform, command line, and a minimal
reproducer.

